## Code Cleanup

### Rendering (crates/scriptbots-render/src/lib.rs)

**Removed unused field**:
```rust
// BEFORE:
struct VectorHudState {
    avg_velocity: (f32, f32),  // Never read after computation
    mean_speed: f32,
    // ...
}

// AFTER:
struct VectorHudState {
    mean_speed: f32,  // avg_velocity removed
    // ...
}
```

Only `mean_speed` and `vector_magnitude` (derived from avg_velocity components) are used for rendering. The intermediate `(avg_vx, avg_vy)` tuple was dead weight.

